thread.title_full: OpenGov raises $25 million, snags Marc Andreessen for board - San Francisco Chronicle

author: Joe Garofoli
title: OpenGov raises $25 million, snags Marc Andreessen for board
text: OpenGov, the Redwood City company whose online tool helps track how government spends tax dollars, has raised a $25 million round of investment and will welcome venture capitalist Marc Andreessen to its board of directors.
